methods.onShutdown:
Hook for shutting down an installation-specific environment for a given process. This is intended for controlled
 invocation, rather than as part of a shutdown hook - onStartup() should setup any mandatory shutdown
 hooks, and code in said shutdown hooks should be idempotent w.r.t. onShutdown().
methods.onStartup: Hook for setting up an installation-specific environment for a given process.
